  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>KIPIDON:</u></strong><u> <strong>We Will Always Love You</strong></u> is an arcade shooter where you shoot everyone to make them feel love again!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/c9d34bcad1e000345aa35ed4a2377dc2.gif?t=1767312863\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/c9d34bcad1e000345aa35ed4a2377dc2.poster.avif?t=1767312863\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/2bdb93d7dcd5f4995625503dc667594c.poster.avif?t=1767312863\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/2bdb93d7dcd5f4995625503dc667594c.webm?t=1767312863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/2bdb93d7dcd5f4995625503dc667594c.mp4?t=1767312863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/2f94de701966f0b3e096e3a59c265ad5.poster.avif?t=1767312863\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/2f94de701966f0b3e096e3a59c265ad5.webm?t=1767312863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/2f94de701966f0b3e096e3a59c265ad5.mp4?t=1767312863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using a <u>cupid's arrow type flower weapon</u>, <strong>explore</strong> <strong>unique and vibrant cities</strong> while <strong>shooting as many people as possible</strong> <strong>before time runs out</strong>!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/481b4b871d203295c81bd4374b83c094.gif?t=1767312863\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/481b4b871d203295c81bd4374b83c094.poster.avif?t=1767312863\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=196 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/a901f1eaa2f9af245f68757b9df39a64.poster.avif?t=1767312863\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/a901f1eaa2f9af245f68757b9df39a64.webm?t=1767312863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/a901f1eaa2f9af245f68757b9df39a64.mp4?t=1767312863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Venus</strong>, the <u>God of Love</u>, has slacked off on his duties, so he calls upon the first two people he can find, <strong>Bèl</strong> & <strong>Chime</strong>, to help him catch up!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embark</strong> on this <u>downright incomprehensible</u> story, featuring a variety of <u>Electronic</u>, <u>Bossa-Nova</u>, <u>HipHop</u>, and <u>experimental</u> tunes composed by award nominated musician, <strong>ClascyJitto</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/7532b2fc515945fcda443dd8e9519557.apng?t=1767312863\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578160/extras/7532b2fc515945fcda443dd8e9519557.poster.avif?t=1767312863\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=256 /></picture></span></p>",
